    {
      "id": "33",
      "name": "Gallery",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "gallery_character",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/21/25750596/d1bb7ec9ceccf9758053aa0ed34fbf09_9056100509467200233.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>After using and summoning the Serenitea Pot, Travelers can interact with it and enter the abode within.</p><p>Travelers can also use and summon the pot while they are within its confines. Interacting with the Serenitea Pot in this state will allow Travelers to leave it.</p><p>Travelers can also directly open the map interface and fast travel to any of the Teleport Waypoints to immediately leave the Serenitea Pot.</p>",
                "key": "Page 1/9"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/21/25750596/97b4b55c929db9eaf9ef438f8f18b3b4_3364168253942108304.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Talk to the <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">teapot spirit</span> inside the <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Serenitea Pot</span> to learn about and manage all manner of teapot-related affairs.</p>",
                "key": "Page 2/9"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/21/25750596/326e4ddae739da5c55e3d132309ef581_6376819081415061405.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>You can create all kinds of items from the Creation Screen.</p>",
                "key": "Page 3/9"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/21/25750596/6248324f6b8057557d6871ea32c23c4b_2518452467102661845.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Materials used to create items can be gathered all over the world.</p>",
                "key": "Page 4/9"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/21/25750596/f016c4cb1effb82035cf9d8a0b9e222d_6212332068391781555.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>After obtaining a furnishing, use the Place function to put it in position.</p>",
                "key": "Page 5/9"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/21/25750596/ac58638274c6b8b29d8a06191cf98071_4652137589489170648.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Place furnishings to increase the <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Adeptal Energy Rank</span> of your Serenitea Pot. As your Adeptal Energy Rank increases, Realm Currency will accumulate at a faster rate.</p>",
                "key": "Page 6/9"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/21/25750596/b6e632172830fcb550fc2391b99f0d4e_3810335948400628949.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Spend <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Realm Currency</span> in the <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Realm Depot</span> to purchase various items.</p>",
                "key": "Page 7/9"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/21/25750596/8a14725abeeba03dc5faed31fa057655_7660664317369616272.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Once in a while, a Teapot Traveling Salesman will visit your abode. There is a chance that he will bring some rare treasures with him.</p>",
                "key": "Page 8/9"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/21/25750596/2237ab5a1d18dd3ee5490d5b5b1bfd10_8819134079753971602.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>If you acquire the blueprint for a Furnishing Set, you can place furnishings by batch. You can still make adjustments to individual furnishings when batch-placing them.</p>",
                "key": "Page 9/9"
              }
            ],
            "pic": ""
          }
        }
      ]
